          <p class="text-sm text-text-light">Självtömmande station — töm påsen bara var 30–60 dag.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/robotdammsugare-storlagenhet/" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-5 hover:border-accent transition-colors group">
